<HL>
   France's Military
   Shipbuilders Trying
   To Cut Bureaucracy
   ---
   Their Goal Is to Establish
   Commercial Export Unit
   For Flexibility and Profit
   ----
   By E.S. Browning
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
09/24/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), NO PAGE CITATION
</SO>
